abstract="Serious Games are full-fledged games that aim at accomplishing a double mission: to achieve the serious goal without compromising the experience of playing a game (player experience, PX). To develop high-quality Serious Games, an interdisciplinary approach is required which integrates computer science, technology and design, psychology, and pedagogy as well as insights from the application domain.",
isbn="978-3-030-35048-2"
